Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,NO ENTRY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That took long enough. I can finally take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to rush to the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission was to stop the Others's advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Captain Shiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Captain Shiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:00:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You should take a break sometimes,\NCaptain Shiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd become a captain someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Train the new recruits and pay attention\Nto their performances,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,those are what a captain does.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane was supposed to be the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want her to take your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, she got her hands full already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't ask her to take over the platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you discussing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not working here today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to submit a progress report.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you discussing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We were talking about what makes a good captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have other plans today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito is coming here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go pick him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to do very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫How do you still create\Na relationship each other♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s my awkward friend’s fault♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone somewhere\Nto embrace me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫While the devil is not here\Nand between the chaos♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now,\NI’m trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:03:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’ll see I’m always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and your roller coaster\Ninside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and\Nthe unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫To pierce with the theory♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and the theory in the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"EVERYONE'S FUTURE"\NIt's not being used anymore, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You should listen to your doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you choose to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Arashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She said this place was too noisy to take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here for the retirement paperwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I also came here to check on everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a lot of new faces around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been many new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Extinction Belt is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are still come remaining Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Shiden became a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become a major general or even the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You? As the chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The tension between Suoh and Seiran\Nhas never ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be more cooperation\Nbetween the two cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The people will be in a lot of trouble\Nif someone who doesn't know it becomes a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to keep going on missions before\NI received the official retirement order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure OSF won't go astray again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel relieved with you guys around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome to drop by anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we throw another dumpling party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself, just don't order too much food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To the destruction of Kunad Gate, cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The dumplings were delicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but there were too many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You ate plenty of them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't waste food for no good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Hanabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice Platoon will be on patrol missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to her now if you want to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice Platoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi, Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding the inhumane experiment\Nconducted at the OSF hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-the chief of the hospital has...\N-What my uncle did at the facility
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,was never known to my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They were more worried about me, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a challenging future ahead\Nfor the Ichijo family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But perhaps that's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But things are even tougher for Captain Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because the Chairman of OSF hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is Captain Alice's elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you holding up, Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Sumeragi has been replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on his statement during the hearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,he will face punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Extinction Belt may be gone now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Sumeragi family has faced public uproar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, we cannot dwell on the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I was scouted into the OSF,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but fighting along everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and creating a better future\Nfor the sake of New Himuka
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is still very meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Extinction Belt has been eliminated,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the sunlight has become warmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The plants are very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do my best to give them
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a peaceful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, Yuito,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,how are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you are retiring.\NWe're going to miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki and Captain Alice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,are finally getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The marriage was arranged a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really that big of a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be sure to attend your wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make the bouquet for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that is one way to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now is not the right time for a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can invite only the people from HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll consider that idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane, see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You people are always so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're finally discharged, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's one burden taken off my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be really worried about\NMajor General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the time to be concerned\Nabout his business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on the promotion,\NMajor General Luka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really retiring?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to learn more about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to help make this country a better place
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,as a member of the OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This country is not a friendly place\Nfor Bell Peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our system has ignored them completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We pretend like they don't exist at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Without brain power, they can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I had gone through that as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to develop my power,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent every day inside the lab
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and suffered in loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Luka?\N-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there was a boy just like me\Nwho was also a test subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to survive\Nthose experiments thanks to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I can't even remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's hope for the best for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Kasane.\NWe don't know how the project will go,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems everyone has really forgotten him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't remember anything about Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day, history was rewritten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we the only people who remember Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because we connected ourselves to\NYuito and Kasane through SAS?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the wielder of Red Strings,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we have become the people\Nwho can observe the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, how is your body holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped having headache after that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use my power with no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because the Kunad Gate has been destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case is, this is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi, a little to the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't get used to\Nhaving Alice in the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been here since you joined the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be from the other platoon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always been here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What were we talking about just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned the causality\Nbetween Karen's time jump
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and Alice being alive all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything else after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the incident\Ncaused a massive butterfly effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have no way to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He sacrificed himself to create a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who sacrificed himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't like making baseless assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen is slowly being wiped\Nfrom everyone's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito! Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, only we remember the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen has been erased from everyone's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the world he wanted to create.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than Alice being alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,everything else remains unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I still think Karen's was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Changing the history for the sake of a loved one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,should not be allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, we are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen was the one who created this reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But we will
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,create the future for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll create our own future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the long wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that coffee for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, you are still a soldier of OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll retain my ranks until\Nthe other preparation is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The saviors of our country are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I say "traitors?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero and Kyoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you're doing well, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two taking part\Nin the Moon investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The New Himuka government wanted our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We disbanded the Togestsu Faith too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When BABE stopped operating,\Nthe cryosleep devices also stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All the immigrants from Moon woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Without BABE, they are not a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The government has no records of you two\Nbeing Togetsu spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a deal between the adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They will require the knowledge\Nand information you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If the information we have\Ncan help in any way,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the government will have our full support.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yuito, regarding our father...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Sumeragi knew\Nabout those inhuman experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:15:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But he also protected New Himuka from Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We will spread the word around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, what will you do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if everything goes well after the project?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go back to the Moon if you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer have the intention to go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a reason to go back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am concerned about
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,my family on the Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and what the place has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is no way to go back there just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Kagero decided to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You are at the top of the command chain\Nof the immigrants,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,General Shin Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We are counting on you, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,People from ancient times can be\Nsuch a pain in the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They left behind all those files.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that, General?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hanabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there no way for Yuito's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could stop it back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Yuito, all of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is wrong with Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she thinking anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I want to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Kasane too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she really going to the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of technologies and information\Nleft behind by the immigrants in Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what the Moon has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst case is that\Nit's now crawling with Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, Kasane insists on going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's even going there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you volunteered\Nto be the advance team.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know how it is on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I must take point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We can just send the drones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I run into people who are attacked by Others,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can save them with my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must go there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to have any regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't just stand and do nothing\Nwhile people die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew this would happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I insisted on making you fight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and made you responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate that feeling as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi and I had a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised to become great soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to have any regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, I'm going to become a politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to build a country where its people\Nwon't be monitored
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and lied to by the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make life better for Bell Peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to research on the Other particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Extinction Belt is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There could be a way to turn people\Nback to normal after metamorphosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll create a better future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The OSF can do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be able to retire if we choose to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you could, you wouldn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-right, Shiden?\N-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the future chief after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how far up I'll reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how much longer\Nthis body can hold up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't that different from Kasane\Nwhen you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito must have his own plans as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not the kind who would settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He might actually become a politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let Kasane and Yuito get ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that ignorant brat\Nwill become a politician...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you could show him the way, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You can be his mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that sound, General?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a great idea, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go now and do my best to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't expect anything less from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be a great politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm not very sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I feel worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But even when I'm alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel motivated knowing that everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is still giving their all for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's changing the world\Nis an inflated thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've saved the world once,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can change it for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to college\Nwhile you are going to the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be a great distance between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but we are still in the same world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave this place in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, you can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Others have been spotted in area E-24.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice Platoon, head to the area immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiden Platoon, moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a member of OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of us is a unique individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,people can be connected with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be alone, but not lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU'VE RECEIVED A MESSAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,YUITO SUMERAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,KAITO
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how far apart we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we can't see each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm troubled by my own yearning♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:23:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Unveil the blocked sun ray♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's a stranger in me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫That I've never seen♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I can not soar in the sky without fear♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm spreading my wings♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.13,0:23:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Dancing gracefully like a bird♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And gazing towards the scarlet sky♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I chased after the gust♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The scenery spreads into\Nthe ever-changing world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Inside the intertwined brilliance♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm still searching for tomorrow's direction♫
